<h1>This is Haskell Web Server Application</h1>

<h2>The app dependents on many libraries</h2>

<ul>
<li>Wai - low level Web service API</li>
<li>AESON - Serialize and deserialize Json data</li>
<li>Redis - Key and Value data store. NoSql</li>
<li>Sqlite3 - file-based Relational Data Engine, it is similar to MySql but less functionarities.</li>
<li>more</li>
</ul>

<h1>What the app can do?</h1>

<ul>
<li>Submit data to Server, and store data in database or local file.</li>
<li>Use websocket to send Json</li>
<li>Use Redis to query data from Redis server</li>
</ul>

</body>
